NEXORA AI
Authentication Foundation

Version: 1.0
Status: Ready for Implementation

1. Objective

This document defines the authentication architecture for the NEXORA AI backend.

The authentication system must provide:

Secure login
JWT-based authentication
Role-based authorization
Refresh token support
Password encryption
Email verification
Password reset
Session management
API security
Scalability for future OAuth integration

At the end of this phase, every protected API should require valid authentication.

